  # ABILITIES (COMICAL)
  _basicAttack:
    abilityId: reahu_chomp_miss
    abilityName: Chompy Chomp (Misses Body)
    description: |
      Reahu tries to bite but his food just... falls through his severed 
      neck! "I hate being just a head! I'm SO HUNGRY but I CAN'T EAT!"
    damage: 35
    cooldown: 0
    staminaCost: 5
    range: 3.0
    type: Melee
    element: Shadow
    statusEffects:
      - frustration_damage

  _specialAbility:
    abilityId: reahu_darkness_burp
    abilityName: VOID BURP
    description: |
      Reahu burps up PURE DARKNESS from millions of years ago! 
      "EXCUSE ME! That was the Buddha's first century! Very vintage!" 
      The ancient burp smells like COSMIC DESPAIR!
    damage: 45
    cooldown: 12
    staminaCost: 35
    range: 8
    type: AoE
    element: Shadow
    statusEffects:
      - ancient_burp_cloud
      - existential_dread_debuff

  _ultimateAbility:
    abilityId: reahu_eclipse_tantrum
    abilityName: ECLIPSE TANTRUM
    description: |
      Reahu is SO MAD about being just a head that he throws a COSMIC 
      TANTRUM! He swallows the sun AND moon while screaming "IT'S NOT 
      FAIR! I JUST WANTED A DRINK!" Total eclipse of PURE RAGE!
    damage: 200
    cooldown: 65
    staminaCost: 85
    range: 20
    type: AoE
    element: Shadow
    statusEffects:
      - tantrum_darkness_8s
      - screaming_void
      - everyone_uncomfortable

  _passiveAbility:
    abilityId: reahu_just_a_head
    abilityName: It's Just a Head
    description: |
      Reahu is JUST A HEAD. Enemies keep trying to attack his body 
      and missing! "HA! Where are you hitting? DOWN THERE? I don't 
      HAVE a down there anymore! Joke's on YOU!"
    damage: 0
    cooldown: 0
    staminaCost: 0
    range: 0
    type: Buff
    element: Shadow

  _comboMoves:
    - abilityId: reahu_floating_headbutt
      abilityName: Floating Headbutt
      description: |
        Reahu headbutts enemies! It's ALL he can do! "At least I still 
        have my HEAD! Get it? Because that's all... never mind."
      damage: 40
      cooldown: 0
      staminaCost: 18
      type: Melee
      
    - abilityId: reahu_bite_ankle
      abilityName: Ankle Biter
      description: |
        Reahu floats low and bites ankles! "I used to swallow the SUN! 
        Now I bite ANKLES! How far I've fallen!" CHOMP!
      damage: 100
      cooldown: 20
      staminaCost: 45
      type: Melee

  # PERSONALITY
  _personality:
    bravery: 75
    kindness: 35
    wisdom: 85
    humor: 60
    loyalty: 55
    curiosity: 70

  _likes:
    - Eclipses (obviously)
    - The quiet of deep darkness
    - Philosophical discussions about morality
    - Being proven wrong about himself
    - Second chances

  _dislikes:
    - Bright sunlight (painful)
    - Being called a monster
    - His own past
    - Those who believe evil is permanent
    - Pity

  _favoriteFood: He doesn't need to eat... but misses the sensation
  _hobby: Stargazing and contemplating existence
  _fear: Reverting to his old, hateful self
  _dream: To be remembered as a protector, not a demon

  # VOICE LINES
  _voiceLines:
    lines:
      - type: Greeting
        text: "Do not fear the darkness. Fear what hides within it."
      - type: Greeting
        text: "I am Reahu. Yes, THAT Reahu. Things have... changed."
      - type: Selection
        text: "You would ally with a demon? Bold."
      - type: Selection
        text: "The shadows answer your call."
      - type: BattleStart
        text: "I spent eons destroying. Now I protect."
      - type: BattleStart
        text: "Let me show you productive darkness."
      - type: Attack
        text: "Into the void!"
      - type: Attack
        text: "Darkness consumes!"
      - type: SpecialAttack
        text: "Let shadow embrace you!"
      - type: Ultimate
        text: "WITNESS TOTAL ECLIPSE! THE LIGHT... DIES!"
      - type: Hurt
        text: "I have endured worse... for eternity..."
      - type: LowHealth
        text: "I cannot die... but I can still fall..."
      - type: Victory
        text: "Even demons can be heroes. Remember that."
      - type: Victory
        text: "The darkness protected you today. Ironic."
      - type: Defeat
        text: "Perhaps... I was always meant to fail..."
      - type: LevelUp
        text: "My darkness grows... but so does my control."
      - type: Idle
        text: "*floats silently, contemplating infinity*"
      - type: Idle
        text: "I wonder... do the Sun and Moon remember me?"
      - type: InteractFriendly
        text: "You see past what I was. Thank you."
      - type: InteractRival
        text: "Judge me by my actions, not my nature."
      - type: Funny
        text: "I tried to eat the Sun once. Bad idea. Very hot."

  # RELATIONSHIPS
  _relationships:
    - characterId: mealea_apsara
      characterName: Mealea
      type: Rival
      affinity: 40
      relationshipDescription: |
        As a being of Light, Mealea's presence is literally painful for Reahu. 
        Yet she's one of the few who believes in his redemption. Their 
        relationship is complex - respect mixed with fundamental opposition.
      specialDialogue:
        - "Apsara... your light burns, but I endure."
        - "You believe I can be good. I'm still not sure you're right."
        - "Perhaps light and dark need not be enemies."

    - characterId: prohm_dino
      characterName: Prohm
      type: Friend
      affinity: 70
      relationshipDescription: |
        Two ancient beings who have existed since before recorded history. 
        Prohm doesn't judge Reahu for his past - he's seen too much to 
        judge anyone.
      specialDialogue:
        - "Ancient One, you have seen much. As have I."
        - "We are both relics. Perhaps that makes us kin."

    - characterId: naga_serpent
      characterName: Naga Prince
      type: Acquaintance
      affinity: 50
      relationshipDescription: |
        The Naga Prince is wary of Reahu but respects his choice to change. 
        Both know what it's like to be feared for what you are.
      specialDialogue:
        - "Serpent Prince, we both know the burden of being... monstrous."
        - "You rule shadows underwater. I rule them everywhere else."

  # BACKSTORY
  _birthplace: The Cosmic Ocean, during the churning of Amrita
  _occupation: Reformed Demon / Eclipse Bringer
  _familyBackground: |
    Originally a powerful Asura (demon). His body still exists somewhere, 
    wandering mindlessly - known as Ketu in some legends.
  _backstory: |
    See full biography above.
  _keyMemories:
    - "Drinking the nectar of immortality and the brief moment of triumph."
    - "The burning pain as Vishnu's discus severed my head."
    - "My first eclipse - swallowing the Sun in rage."
    - "The moment, after a million years, when rage finally faded to sadness."
    - "Choosing to fight the Shadow Serpent - choosing to be more than a demon."

